  "title": "Full-Time Sales Assistant (Clementi, Suntec, Chinatown, Marine Parade & Pasir Ris)",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Clementi, Suntec, Chinatown, Marine Parade & Pasir Ris</strong><br />⏰ 8.30am-5.30pm/ 11am-10pm/ 12pm-10.30pm<br />📅 6-days work week<br />💰 Gross salary up to $3,100/month<br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u><br />• Deliver warm, friendly and professional customer service. <br />• Operate the POS system efficiently and accurately to process cash, cards and digital payments. <br />• Assist customers with placing orders and coordinating the collection of pre-ordered cakes.<br />• Operate the bread slicer machine safely and correctly <em><strong>(training will be provided; strict compliance with safety procedures is required)</strong></em>. <br />• Pack baked products carefully to ensure good presentation, product quality and prevention of damage. <br />• Replenish bread shelves, product displays and cake counters to ensure they are well-stocked, neat and visually appealing. <br />• Maintain a high-level of cleanliness and hygiene in the shop, including counters, equipment and workstations.<br />• Support daily shop operations such as opening and closing duties when required. <br />• Work closely with team members to ensure smooth operations during peak hours.<br />• Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Supervisor/ Manager. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u><br />•<strong> Singaporeans Only</strong><br />• Prior experience in retail, F&B or customer service roles will be an advantages.<br />• Candidates with no prior experience are welcome to apply as training will be provided. <br />• Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment. <br />• Able to multitask and work efficiently while maintaining service quality. <br />• Team-oriented with a positive attitude and willingness to learn.<br />• Able to work shifts, including weekends and public holidays. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Staffs' Benefits:</strong></u><br />• Annual & Medical leaves entitlement <br />• Medical claims <br />• AWS/ VB<br />• Annual salary increment<em><strong> (based on individuals' work performance)</strong></em><br />• Attendance, weekends & public holiday shift allowances<br />• OT payable <br /></p><p>📱Interested applicants can <strong>WhatsApp @ 84944246 </strong>OR <strong>Tele: @fourleaveshr</strong></p>",
